    "created_at": "2016-08-02T23:45:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-02T23:47:03Z",
    "body": "I'm hoping there's a low-level command to force the Windows pop-up until [the upstream issue](https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=497381) is completely resolved. Even if it's relatively hacky, it'd be better than not being able to input text. Conversely, being able to disable it completely would provide a way to work around it in the mean time.\n\nBecause it's a blocker for those that need the keyboard (where a hardware keyboard isn't possible or probable), is it worth re-classifying this @zcbenz?\n"
